<plot>A powerful blend of education, drama and real-life stories reveals secrets about the drug MDMA (Methylene-Dioxy-Methamphetamine), commonly known as Ecstasy. What are the real effects of Ecstasy? What "techniques" are used to gets kids to buy it? This video unlocks the untold story of this drug as you witness former Ecstasy dealers and users tell their real-life stories. You will also see what happens to a dealer's life and the fate of his friends and customers.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?663011</url></doc>
